Equity Bank of Kenya CEO Says He Reduced Shareholding to Comply With Law

-- B y   J o h n s t o n e   O l e   T u r a n a
-- 
2011-03-18T06:00:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/equity-bank-of-kenya-ceo-says-he-reduced-shareholding-to-comply-with-law.html
  Equity Bank Ltd. (EQBNK)  Chief Executive
Officer said he reduced his stake in the bank to 5 percent from
7.2 percent to comply with Kenyan law.  The East African nation’s Banking Act bars the management
of lenders from owning more than 5 percent of their company’s
stock, Mwangi told investors today at a briefing in Nairobi, the
capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
